##This 6-year-old Shanghai child child becomes the "little reporter" with the brush in the war-stricken rear area!

Micro Signal Xinminzhoukan

Function description, depth and angle —— this is what we can do.

SISTER-IN-LAW IN THE WAR "epidemic" front battle, have done the war behind the "small reporters. The change of painting content also quietly tells the change of epidemic situation.

Editor's note

While many kids enjoy winter break, one called Youyou finds an interesting and persistent thing to do -- call it fighting the flu.
Yes, your name is Cai Yicheng. She is a 6-year-old girl who likes to draw.
The baby's brother-in-law (that is, the baby's mother's aunt) is Yan Chai Hospital breathing Doctor Cha Qiongfang, she in the New Year's Eve with the first aid team Hubei Medical Expedition in Wuhan. Because of the aunt's departure, the children of the new crown pneumonia epidemic development is particularly concerned about, but also particularly concerned about the battle in the front-line sister-in-law.
The painting started with her mother-in-law, who then began to look through the daily news to find the material for the painting. Every day at noon and evening news is a must see, the Shanghai News to see the end, but also to see the CCTV, often see the news she is interested in the content, she asked her mother to take pictures.
Now she still eagerly look forward to "painting time" every day, she is like a small reporter, with painting this special way to "report" the development of the epidemic. Family members are laughing: brother-in-law in the war "epidemic" front battle, there are doing the war behind the "small reporters. The changes in the content of the paintings also speak quietly about the changes in the epidemic situation: from the initial hospital construction to all kinds of material support, from the care of the isolation point to the patient's discharge from the hospital in succession, i believe that soon we can see the medical team triumphantly returning to Wuhan, a beautiful picture of spring flowers blooming.
The longest winter vacation in history will leave a deep impression on her, and these pictures will not only become a precious memory of her life, but also leave us a lovely and touching record.
